(226, 1, '2016-01-18 11:01:24', '2016-01-18 19:01:24', '<h2>More Information</h2>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<h4>Digital Template</h4>\r\nThis item is a digital template. To edit this template, simply use our online design application in your browser, make the necessary changes, and save the PDF. <strong>You don''t need any special software on your computer to edit this template. </strong>If you ever need to make changes to the template again, just login and your template will be waiting for you. You can make unlimited revisions.\r\n<h4>Changing Colors</h4>\r\nYou are free to change colors of the design, text, and background to anything you''d like. It''s very easy!\r\n<h4>Printing</h4>\r\nAfter making changes to the template and saving the PDF file you can choose to print it on your home printer or take it to any print shop or office supply store like Kinkos®, Office Depot®, Office Max®, Staples®, etc. For all templates smaller than 8 1/2" x 11" a home printer is usually perfect. For larger templates, a print shop may be necessary. The PDF file is in high quality 300 dpi resolution.\r\n<h4>Trimming</h4>\r\nAfter printing, simply trim the template along the crop marks and make any folds if required.', 'More Info', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', 'tab_569d36841fa9f', 'more-info', '', '', '2016-02-09 19:36:12', '2016-02-10 03:36:12', '', 0, 'http://youprintem.com/?post_type=wc_product_tab&#038;p=226', 0, 'wc_product_tab', '', 0),
